& [SLMSlice28PrimerProviderEvidence] is the source-complete slice for provider evidence in compact primers
  + [slice_id] is SLM-28
  + [status] is source_complete_policy_gated
  + [effort] is S
  + [risk] is medium
  + [depends_on] is SLM-10, SLM-22, SLM-26, SLM-27
  + [contract] is slm_project/specifications/contracts/SLM_Primer_Provider_Evidence_Contract.sop
  + [deliverable] is compact primer provider suggestion and deliberation evidence
  + [completion_review] is slm_project/planning/project_manager/reviews/SLM_Manager_Batch_Review_2026-06-21.sop

  & [WorkCompleted] is the slice result
    + [added] is provider_suggestion compact evidence items
    + [updated] is provider_deliberation refs to include objection, answer, jury, and faculty report refs

  & [RemainingGate] is executable verification
    + [blocked_by] is Windows Application Control policy for Cargo-generated executables
    + [allowed_validation] is source scan and SOP review only
